Description: Voice dictation and transcription GUI for Linux (STT)
 Turbo Whisper is a SuperWhisper-like voice dictation application for Linux.
 It provides speech to text (STT) transcription using OpenAI Whisper API or
 self-hosted faster-whisper-server. Voice typing made easy with a beautiful GUI.
 .
 Features:
  - Global hotkey to start/stop recording from anywhere
  - Animated waveform visualization (OpenAI/ElevenLabs style orb)
  - OpenAI Whisper API compatible (works with self-hosted servers)
  - Auto-types transcribed text into focused window
  - System tray integration
  - Clipboard support
 .
 Perfect for voice input with AI CLI tools like Claude Code, Aider,
 GitHub Copilot CLI, and terminal applications. Great for accessibility
 and hands-free typing.
 .
 Keywords: voice dictation, speech to text, stt, whisper gui, transcription,
 voice typing, voice input, dictation software, speech recognition, accessibility,
 transcribe audio, hands-free, superwhisper alternative
